						<div class="postbody">- During a sprite DMA transfer (4014h), does the PPU run? Can IRQs/NMI be requested/triggered during this period?
<br />
<br />- What cycle and line does the PPU render its first visible background pixel? And when does it plot into screen?
<br />
<br />- Thanks. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_razz.gif" alt=":P" title="Razz" /></div>

					
